Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.41,0:01:18.16,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}于是牵住了伙伴的手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.87,0:01:24.09,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}这样的话将永远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.34,0:01:29.05,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}活在童年无忧的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.05,0:01:36.72,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}无论如何都想要告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.14,0:01:42.86,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}伙伴们曾牵在一起的手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.27,0:01:49.53,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}已变得七零八落
