Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//--------------------ED--------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.32,0:19:46.30,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}哪怕忘了这一切  也能生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.69,0:19:59.56,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不过每当再次回想起来  总会留下铭心的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.56,0:20:11.62,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}只好流着泪不断安慰自己「这样就好」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:23.86,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}若能有一个不留遗憾的结局的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:31.97,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}为了谁我们不断前行？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.97,0:20:38.91,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}为了谁我们再次醒来？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.08,0:20:52.54,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不管有没有人  依然给予鼓励
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.73,0:21:19.27,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}把心封闭起来也没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.27,0:21:31.77,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}只要拥有那最珍贵的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.11,0:21:37.92,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}总有一天会察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.08,0:21:44.12,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}朝阳是如此的耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.69,0:21:56.52,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}站在身旁的是已成长起来的你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.20,0:22:04.38,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}为了谁我们不断前行？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.38,0:22:11.67,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}为了谁我们再次醒来？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.67,0:22:25.45,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不管还有没有人 依然在等待着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.07,0:22:40.59,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}LaLaLa…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:55.14,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不管有没有人  我们依然高歌
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//--------------------TEXT--------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.69,0:00:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介已经好几天都闭门不出了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.63,0:00:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么  我无从得知
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.67,0:00:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.47,0:00:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着我  恭介
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.32,0:00:29.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会再一次建立Little Busters
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.77,0:00:34.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我将大家带到恭介的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.28,0:00:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介一定会露出笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.10,0:00:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像曾经那样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.19,0:02:33.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来该拉谦吾入伙了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.96,0:02:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是谦吾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙可不好对付  恐怕不会轻易就加入
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.02,0:02:40.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.87,0:02:44.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介当初是怎么拉拢谦吾的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得小时候的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.71,0:02:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介当时去踢馆了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.22,0:02:50.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,踢馆？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某天出现了这样的传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:02:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说本市有个小学生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.21,0:03:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在全国少年啥啥的剑道大赛上胜出
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.87,0:03:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是谦吾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:07.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一跃成为全市的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.81,0:03:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且他家本身就开着道场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以恭介想到去踢馆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.83,0:03:16.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「有人么」这么说道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他跟谦吾的老爸打了一场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.53,0:03:20.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟他父亲？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.96,0:03:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.44,0:03:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之他老爸是师傅  超厉害的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为打倒了他老爸  所以谦吾成了伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.59,0:03:30.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.40,0:03:48.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  谦吾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.31,0:03:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.38,0:03:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得以前恭介去踢馆的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:04:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介为什么不挑战你  而去挑战你的父亲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.74,0:04:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树  我有言在先
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:07.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.52,0:04:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会加入Little Busters
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就别幻想能再进一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谦吾看穿了我想要做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介  我进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你醒着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.99,0:04:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想哭诉一番
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:05:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但恭介正因什么而受到伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.06,0:05:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须坚强起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是来看看你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.29,0:05:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃饭  不然对身体不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:25.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谦吾  说了一个谎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.75,0:05:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚刚说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  恭介这么说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他告诉我  谦吾在说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实他是双胞胎经常换人之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.41,0:05:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实他有60岁  满口都是假牙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谦吾  你刚想用右手来翻书吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们在看  所以换回左手了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:12.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:15.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想用右手  却停住了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.21,0:06:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤已经好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:20.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抑或是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.54,0:06:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就没受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.69,0:06:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要骗我们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是因为受伤才放弃新人战的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是不想参加吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我回答你这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:39.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就肯放弃拉我加入Little Busters吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.25,0:06:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谦吾一定知道我所不知道的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟发生了什么  告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我们变得七零八落
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.67,0:06:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样走下去  最后到达的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.70,0:07:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里等待你的  是一片黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没必要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.92,0:07:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只需要快乐地玩下去就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.08,0:07:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家失去了笑容  恭介变得那样落魄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要让我快乐起来  我办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想让大家重新笑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.34,0:07:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像曾经恭介所做的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.01,0:07:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.55,0:07:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就在此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:31.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分道扬镳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超越我吧  理树
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.14,0:08:04.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾几何时  我发过誓的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要成为不输给恭介的领袖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.69,0:08:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算怎么办  理树
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.90,0:08:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝不会放弃Little Busters
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:25.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这样谦吾就会离开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.03,0:08:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不准
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.14,0:08:29.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两件事能兼得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.92,0:08:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会去实现  不管用什么方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.85,0:08:39.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用实力打倒他  他就会加入
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谦吾会这么单纯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定他其实挺单纯的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是个笨蛋嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.31,0:08:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  我能打倒谦吾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.44,0:08:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从小到大他都从未有过败绩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.44,0:08:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我连剑道的竹刀都没握过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.36,0:09:01.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用棒球决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.37,0:09:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是不久前才开始玩扔接球的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.22,0:09:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许会是场不错的比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.46,0:09:19.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.47,0:09:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不比一比怎么知道结果
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.53,0:09:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.63,0:09:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  既然说定了就来练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.80,0:09:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谦吾  找你好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.05,0:09:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.70,0:09:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会放弃  我要向你挑战棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:57.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认真比一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:03.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我赢了  谦吾就要加入Little Busters
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清楚了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.02,0:10:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天放学后在操场等你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.97,0:10:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树  你不知道这个世界的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.73,0:10:23.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样的事情已经重复过无数遍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.74,0:10:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你却全都忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.05,0:10:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来打棒球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.12,0:10:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树来向我挑战棒球了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜的他  连那天的比赛也忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.51,0:10:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让队友来扔球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.52,0:11:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能首先将球打出场外三回的队伍胜出
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.69,0:11:10.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.05,0:11:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了保护铃和理树  与你战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要来了  谦吾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.81,0:11:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能打中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.07,0:11:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古式…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.40,0:11:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你现在会出现在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.74,0:11:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然玩这种把戏！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.94,0:11:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.86,0:11:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜负已定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.58,0:11:58.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你用了禁忌的招数
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.04,0:12:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利用理树不知道的这个世界的构造
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.15,0:12:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欺骗了我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.44,0:12:06.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不惜践踏我心中的伦理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.22,0:12:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成自己一手策划的剧本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.93,0:12:11.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可结果又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.34,0:12:16.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把理树和铃丢进了黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.18,0:12:20.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之所以会变成这副窝囊样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.75,0:12:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为计划惨遭失败后的自责
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.07,0:12:29.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.32,0:12:31.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树和铃很弱小
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.01,0:12:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们还是只会逃避的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须好好保护
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.16,0:12:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能永远都是孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.46,0:12:43.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人是会成长的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.50,0:12:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个封闭的世界里？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.40,0:12:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取胜之后告诉理树
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.34,0:13:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「你只要被我们保护着  快乐地玩下去就行了」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.64,0:13:20.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在赢下这场比赛后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:23.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会竭尽全力保护你和铃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我还能在这个世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:39.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一对一互相投球
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.87,0:13:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先打出本垒打的获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:48.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正面还是反面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.69,0:13:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是反面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我选后攻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裁判和捕手由我担任
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:00.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,击不击球自己判断
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.55,0:14:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但漏过三个好球的话就算三振出局哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.69,0:14:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许你现在十分害怕我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.02,0:14:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但在比赛结束后我将会是你的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.76,0:14:15.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好感受一下我的可靠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.93,0:14:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.15,0:14:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.57,0:14:26.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树  不挥棒是打不到球的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫无悬念的比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.53,0:14:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我赢定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.92,0:14:35.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.43,0:14:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.10,0:14:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此结束也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.77,0:14:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以结束
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.53,0:14:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没击中  三振
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.93,0:15:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微擦到一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.44,0:15:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是界外球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.55,0:15:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还算打到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.52,0:15:09.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不能就这样结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.58,0:15:13.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么说  已经两个好球了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.02,0:15:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.82,0:15:17.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:21.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,界外球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.22,0:15:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是界外球
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.27,0:15:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.66,0:15:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.03,0:15:54.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.08,0:15:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要纠缠不放
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.96,0:16:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用面对现实
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.41,0:16:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我来保护你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:12.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要让谦吾变成伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让大家再次聚在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我才是Little Busters的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.31,0:16:22.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,领袖啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:37.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.70,0:16:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了  成功了  成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.09,0:16:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然把一切都复位是不可能办到的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.40,0:16:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没完
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.44,0:16:55.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也打出全垒打就是平局了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.12,0:17:00.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题吧  理树
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.84,0:17:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经耗尽全力了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我还能继续
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.57,0:17:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂停
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.02,0:17:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,投手换人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.24,0:17:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,投手换人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:30.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是在危急关头出现  才叫王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.79,0:17:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是我和理树认真在比的比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.75,0:17:37.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.25,0:17:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树都竭尽全力面对了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.04,0:17:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会拿出真本事战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.99,0:17:47.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谦吾  我想和铃一起努力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.85,0:17:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们  果然是相连的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便在现在也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.06,0:17:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  就把你们两个一起解决了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.73,0:18:01.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.98,0:18:03.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  谦吾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.78,0:18:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此  理树你来做捕手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.78,0:18:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比赛再次开始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:25.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.28,0:18:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.60,0:18:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不像话的高射炮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  铃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肩膀放松一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肩膀…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.78,0:18:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.78,0:18:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.22,0:19:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,界外球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.27,0:19:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没必要去打坏球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:07.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  铃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坏球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这次很接近好球了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越投越好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.52,0:19:18.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.73,0:19:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像理树一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.26,0:19:30.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,界外球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.70,0:19:33.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的如果没被击中就是好球了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.10,0:19:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好球…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.58,0:19:39.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还是高位的绝好球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.35,0:19:42.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么没能打出本垒打
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个好球了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.08,0:19:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还剩一球了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.65,0:19:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还剩一球了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.30,0:19:50.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被逼入绝境了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.82,0:19:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我居然慌了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.68,0:19:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被他俩的快乐给压倒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.19,0:20:02.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我至今为止的人生都只是为了胜利而活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.73,0:20:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拥有着坚韧的肉体和精神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.48,0:20:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场比赛的胜利必定属于我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.58,0:20:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢从这儿看到的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛某处看到过的天空一般
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.66,0:20:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.67,0:20:25.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃君  就算你的球被打到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.65,0:20:27.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也会在身后保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.46,0:20:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.71,0:20:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快投啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.96,0:20:31.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我们  相信伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.22,0:20:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.00,0:20:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.81,0:20:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们尽情地做自己力所能及的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.37,0:20:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.39,0:20:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正中间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.87,0:20:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我赢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.85,0:21:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好一个雷神喵喵球
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.71,0:21:03.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好球  击球手出局
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.25,0:21:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比赛结束啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.59,0:21:07.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我居然…输了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.05,0:21:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是无敌的  在此本应轻松获得胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.52,0:21:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.69,0:21:26.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我全部的人生都为了获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样  我打败你的老爸了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有人能够把你束缚在胜负中了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.20,0:21:44.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实你也想像笨蛋一样快乐地玩耍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.86,0:21:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.20,0:21:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是棗恭介
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.30,0:21:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天起我们就是朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.50,0:21:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谦吾  跟我一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.09,0:21:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  带我出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.24,0:21:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.09,0:22:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.00,0:22:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是悔恨的泪水
